# Copy this to ".env" and fill in your DeepSeek API key.
# You can also paste it in Settings -> AI Provider after the app starts.
#
# This build uses LOCAL Whisper for transcription (offline, bundled
# next to the .exe) and DeepSeek for the answers. No other services.

# --- DeepSeek (cloud LLM) ---
# Get a key at https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys
# ~$0.14 per million tokens for deepseek-chat (cents per interview).
#   deepseek-chat     - V3, fast, OpenAI-class. Default / recommended.
#   deepseek-reasoner - R1, reasoning model. Slower but stronger.
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=
# Optional overrides:
# DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com/v1
# DEEPSEEK_MODEL=deepseek-chat
